[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    141[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    142[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   11. **The Information Blocking rule's disclosure-accounting obligations require a structural record of certain cross-organizational disclosures.** The architecture should specify the Information-Blocking-rule disclosure-accounting log as a separately-governed compliance artifact.
