[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    634[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Recipe 11.9 is publishable at the complex-regulated tier level once the three HIGH findings are closed. The Honest Take is the recipe's strongest single passage and the chapter's strongest single articulation of the institutional-content-as-substance-conversational-layer-as-interface primitive in cross-organizational longitudinal clinical software context. The "build the institutional muscles for the harder parts first; the conversational layer is the easier part" framing is the chapter's strongest single architectural-priority-as-deployment-strategy moment and matches the chapter pattern from 11.6, 11.7, and 11.8 while elevating the recipe-distinct care-coordination-assistant contributions.
