[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    636[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The recipe-specific contributions that should be elevated to the chapter preface as load-bearing primitives are: (a) the **cross-organizational-data-integration-as-architectural-primitive primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; the integration layer is the bot's architectural floor and the largest single engineering investment); (b) the **longitudinal-coordination-state-as-system-of-record primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; the coordination state is its own record class distinct from any single EHR's chart); (c) the **provenance-as-architectural-primitive primitive** (recipe-distinct; every coordination-state assertion cites its provenance with the source system, message ID, timestamp, and integrity hash); (d) the **referral-and-transition-of-care-state-machines-as-deterministic-institutional-content primitive** (recipe-distinct; the LLM operates on top of state machines with clinical-leadership signoff); (e) the **seam-detection-rule-engine-with-named-clinical-leadership-ownership-per-rule primitive** (recipe-distinct; the rule library is the recipe's distinctive value layer with sampled review for precision and recall); (f) the **caregiver-as-first-class-participant-identity-model primitive** (recipe-distinct; caregivers have separate identities, separate authentication, separate consent posture, and separate state-law access rules); (g) the **cross-organizational-consent-posture primitive** (recipe-distinct; per-data-source and per-sharing-relationship consent with state-specific sensitive-record category enforcement); (h) the **Information-Blocking-rule-and-TEFCA-alignment-posture primitive** (recipe-distinct; the assistant's data integration and data sharing operate within the federal interoperability framework); (i) the **outcome-correlation-against-coordination-specific-outcomes primitive** (recipe-distinct; referral closure rate, transition-of-care completion rate, medication-reconciliation accuracy, avoidable-readmission rate, avoidable-ED-utilization rate, patient-and-caregiver-reported coordination experience, caregiver-burden trajectory, total cost of care); (j) the **hybrid-AI-plus-human-coordination-as-dominant-production-pattern primitive** (recipe-distinct; AI assistant for the broad-middle population with human care managers for high-risk members and escalations); (k) the **multi-quarter-to-multi-year-outcome-demonstration-with-attribution-caveats primitive** (recipe-distinct; coordination outcomes show up over weeks to years depending on the metric); (l) the **narrow-start-with-single-transition-and-narrow-population-before-expanding deployment-strategy primitive** (recipe-distinct; validates architecture before launching with multi-transition multi-population deployment); (m) the **David-as-canonical-multi-condition-multi-organization-user primitive** (recipe-distinct; the canonical case grounds the recipe's moral case for the project); (n) the **build-institutional-muscles-for-harder-parts-first-conversational-layer-is-easier-part primitive** (recipe-distinct architectural-priority-as-deployment-strategy thesis); (o) the **integration-coverage-disparity-as-equity-acute-metric primitive** (recipe-distinct; well-instrumented vs partially-instrumented vs poorly-instrumented patients have substantially different assistant capability and the equity exposure is recipe-acute); (p) the **care-management-workforce-as-dominant-operational-expense primitive** (recipe-distinct; the workforce is typically larger than the AWS infrastructure cost and is the dominant operational expense); (q) the **regulatory-team-from-architectural-design primitive** (recipe-distinct; coordination-software regulatory landscape includes HIPAA and Information Blocking and TEFCA and 42 CFR Part 2 and state-specific sensitive-record protections and FDA SaMD where applicable, with the institutional regulatory team involved from architectural design).
